<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bond-n">bond <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɒnd/    美 /bɑːnd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>黏合；纽带；关系：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This new glue makes a firmer bond. 
这种新胶水粘得更牢固。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a close / an emotional bond 
紧密的关系/情感纽带</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In some cultures friendship means a strong lifelong <strong>bond between</strong> two people. 
在有些文化中友谊就是两个人之间终生的深厚关系。</p></div></div>